The withdrawal can be completed after the MIN_WITHDRAWAL_DELAY_BLOCKS via either of the completeQueuedWithdrawal methods. While in the queue, these shares are removed from the staker's balance, as well as from their operator's delegated share balance (if applicable). Note that while in the queue, deposit shares are still subject to slashing. If any slashing has occurred, the shares received may be less than the queued deposit shares.
